            "    if;v('Month') == 3",
            "      e;Lord;Smile",
            "      s;Lord;So, {e:v('JagenPronouns')['Address1C']} {v:JagenName}, how has your time in Chronos been thus far?",
            "      e;Player;Smile",
            "      s;Player;It's been a pleasant experience, thank you.{w}{c:e;Player;HalfCloseEyes} However{tgm}...",
            "      e;Lord;NoSmile",
            "      s;Lord;Hm?",
            "      e;Player;CloseEyes",
            "      s;Player;Before I came here, I've had very strange dreams.|{c:e;Player;NormalBlink}They all involved a mysterious voice calling to me.|I couldn't make out what it was saying at first,|but as time went on, everything became more clear and frequent.",
            "      s;Lord;How curious.",
            "      s;Player;Indeed.|It wasn't until the night before our first meeting that the voice was finally coherent.|It asked about the both of us.",
            "      s;Lord;Fascinating. Have you had the dream again since then?",
            "      s;Player;No, I haven't.",
            "      e;Lord;Smile",
            "      s;Lord;This is all so intriguing, {e:v('JagenPronouns')['Address1C']} {v:JagenName}!|I would like to look into your situation, if you don't mind.|Your predicament reminds me of an old legend passed down around these parts.|It would be exciting if it turned out to be true.",
            "      e;Player;Smile",
            "      s;Player;A connossieur of myths and legends, I see.|If it wasn't obvious I was in good company already, it surely is now.",
            "      s;Lord;I am glad to hear that, {e:v('JagenPronouns')['Address1C']} {v:JagenName}.|{c:e;Lord;NoSmile}Ah, I hate to cut this conversation short, but I have other duties to attend to for now.|{c:e;Lord;Smile}Perhaps I can tell you about the legend some other time.",
            "      s;Player;I would appreciate that, {e:v('LordPronouns')['Address']}.",
            "      end_skip",
            "      unlock_support_rank;Lord;Player;C",
            "      sound;Item",
            "      alert;Reached Support rank C!",
            "    elif;v('Month') == 6",
            "      e;Lord;Smile",
            "      s;Lord;{e:v('JagenPronouns')['Address1C']} {v:JagenName}, do you have a moment?|I would love to tell you about that legend we discussed months ago.",
            "      e;Player;Smile",
            "      s;Player;Yes, I am free now. Go on, {e:v('LordPronouns')['Address']}.",
            "      s;Lord;Perfect!{c:e;Lord;CloseEyes,Smile} Now, let's see{tgm}...{tgm} *ahem*|{c:e;Lord;Smile}Many centuries ago, the god of time, Chronos,|bestowed upon the founder of our land, Horatius, the Fire Emblem.|The Fire Emblem has been passed down the royal family for generations.|Horatius himself used its powers to protect the land and its people centuries ago.",
            "      s;Player;I see!|{c:e;Player;NoSmile}Now that you mention it, the voice did refer to the Fire Emblem in my dreams.",
            "      e;Lord;NoSmile",
            "      bop;Lord",
            "      s;Lord;R-Really?! {e:v('JagenPronouns')['Address1C']} {v:JagenName}, this may be a sign of things to come.|The dreams you've had can be no coincidence. I'm certain of it now!",
            "      e;Player;CloseEyes",
            "      s;Player;I fear you may be right.|{c:e;Player;NormalBlink}But, what could all this mean?",
            "      e;Lord;CloseEyes",
            "      s;Lord;I{tgm}...{w}{c:e;Lord;NormalBlink}{tgm} {e:v('JagenPronouns')['Address1C']} {v:JagenName}, this is something I have to confirm for myself.|I apologize. Please excuse me.",
            "      move_portrait;Lord;OffscreenRight",
            "      mirror;Player",
            "      s;Player;{e:v('LordPronouns')['AddressC']}?! {v:LordName}!|{c:e;Player;CloseEyes}What is happening{tgm}...?",
            "      end_skip",
            "      unlock_support_rank;Lord;Player;B",
            "      sound;Item",
            "      alert;Reached Support rank B!",
            "    elif;v('Month') == 9",
            "      s;Player;There you are, {e:v('LordPronouns')['Address']}. Are you alright?",
            "      s;Lord;Hello, {e:v('JagenPronouns')['Address1C']} {v:JagenName}.|{c:e;Lord;CloseEyes}I apologize for our last conversation.|{c:e;Lord;HalfCloseEyes}There is something about the Fire Emblem you should know about.",
            "      s;Player;What is it, {e:v('LordPronouns')['Address']}?",
            "      e;Lord;CloseEyes",
            "      s;Lord;\"The Fire Emblem calls to those tied to calamity.\" That is what the legends say.|{c:e;Lord;HalfCloseEyes}I fear something may happen to you, {e:v('JagenPronouns')['Address1C']} {v:JagenName}{tgm}...",
            "      e;Player;HalfCloseEyes",
            "      s;Player;{e:v('LordPronouns')['Address1C']} {v:LordName}{tgm}...|{c:e;Player;NormalBlink}{tgm}I won't let anything happen to either of us.",
            "      e;Lord;NormalBlink",
            "      s;Lord;{e:v('JagenPronouns')['Address1C']} {v:JagenName}? What are you{tgm}...?",
            "      s;Player;The Fire Emblem--perhaps even Chronos himself--called out to me those nights.|He has his eyes on the both of us.|{c:e;Player;CloseEyes}I don't know what he has planned, but we'll be prepared for it.|{c:e;Player;Smile}Our time together will not be wasted, {e:v('LordPronouns')['Address']}.|We will prevent calamity from happening. I swear it!",
            "      s;Lord;{e:v('JagenPronouns')['Address1C']} {v:JagenName}{tgm}...",
            "      bop;Lord",
            "      e;Lord;Smile",
            "      s;Lord;Yes, you're right! We can do this together!",
